    "sa_expert_reviews_QL9wtg": {
      "type": "sa-expert-reviews",
      "blocks": {
        "block_KFPNrd": {
          "type": "Block",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Yarbo has truly allowed me to become my laziest selfand I don't think you can<br/>put a price on that. Strong winds call for moving paticfurniture.</p>",
            "avatar": "shopify://shop_images/Frame_2036456911.jpg",
            "name": "@Joey",
            "rating": 5
          }
        },
        "block_zywhNG": {
          "type": "Block",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>$65.00 saved today, in the spring it'll be $170.00 saved percut! This thing is<br/>great!</p>",
            "avatar": "shopify://shop_images/Frame_2036456912.jpg",
            "name": "@Steve",
            "rating": 5
          }
        },
        "block_WActLB": {
          "type": "Block",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>I am speechless!<br/>Yarbo delivers one of the best products on the market. I got theleaf blower today and this thing is insanely strong. The quality is at Gerrmans product level(if<br/>you know what I mean) I have a $600 blower and Yarbo is 5x-10x stronger.</p>",
            "avatar": "shopify://shop_images/Frame_2036456913.jpg",
            "name": "@Victor",
            "rating": 5
          }
        },
        "block_YaAPCi": {
          "type": "Block",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>I was talking to my wife about the benefits of, and justifications for buying the YARBO. I really appreciate that I am not risking a fall or other injury while shoveling or snowblowing. Also, I am not out in the cold, uncomfortable or worse, miserable.</p>",
            "avatar": "shopify://shop_images/Frame_2036456916.jpg",
            "name": "@Andrew",
            "rating": 5
          }
        },
        "block_am4rVf": {
          "type": "Block",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>The Yarbo has allowed me to spend more time doingthe things I love to do and<br/>not so much time mowing the yard.</p>",
            "avatar": "shopify://shop_images/Frame_2036456914.jpg",
            "name": "@Travis",
            "rating": 5
          }
        },
        "block_gNtm8b": {
          "type": "Block",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Happy Mother's Day to all mothers out there. spend rmore time with families<br/>because Yarbo helps around the house!</p>",
            "avatar": "shopify://shop_images/Frame_2036456915.jpg",
            "name": "@Adam",
            "rating": 5
          }
        }
      },
